&lt;p&gt;If Luster sounds like the kind of company you would like to work for but there isn&#39;t a current opening that fits, please go ahead and fill out this general application. This is not an application for a specific job and does not guarantee you will be interviewed; however, it will make your details searchable by our Talent Acquisition team so they can find you when an opportunity matches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We still strongly encourage you to continue checking our career site and applying directly to positions you&#39;re interested in. We want to help maximize the possibility of you joining our team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Luster?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Luster, we believe that You&#39;re OK You&#39;re OK yeah you&#39;re good our employees are the heart of our success. We recognize that each team member is not only a professional but a person with diverse roles and responsibilities both within and outside the workplace. Our culture reflects this understanding, fostering an environment where individuals are supported holistically, personally, professionally, and creatively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We describe our workplace culture as one that honors the whole individual. At Luster, this means nurturing an environment where everyone can thrive, bringing their full identity, experiences, and ideas to the table. We recognize the importance of diversity of thought, which leads to more innovative solutions and stronger, more cohesive teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our commitment to diversity and inclusion is not just a statement but a practice. We actively encourage our team members to contribute their unique perspectives, which in turn drives us to achieve greater results. Our projects across sectors such as roads and bridges, transit, aviation, and more are successful because of the diverse experiences, expertise, and viewpoints that each team member brings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Luster isn&#39;t just about getting the job done; it&#39;s about creating an environment where our people feel safe, supported, and challenged to reach new heights. Our leadership is dedicated to providing opportunities for growth in an environment that fosters achievement, collaboration, and innovation. We seek team members who are big thinkers, achievers, and self-starters, those who are always ready to take on the next challenge and say, &quot;Let&#39;s make it happen!&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In line with our mission to deliver exceptional Professional Services, we maintain a strong commitment to upholding Professional Integrity, Client Focus, and Social Responsibility. These values guide us as we act as advocates for our clients, leveraging our expertise and commitment to deliver solutions that exceed expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Luster, we understand that our success is directly tied to the well-being and development of our people. This is why we are committed to creating a workplace that values the whole person, embracing who they are, what they bring, and how they can grow. By doing so, we ensure that our team members are not just employees, but empowered individuals who contribute to the collective success of our company and the communities we serve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Luster is a firm you want to be a part of to build innovative and creative capital improvement projects for current and future generations. It&#39;s an exciting time to be working with Luster!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
